title: Deepika Padukone Might Have Single-Handedly Started A New Colour Trend With This Outfit
text:
A video posted by instylemagazine (@instylemagazine) on Jan 8, 2017 at 11:56pm PST 
Wearing a bright yellow, one-shoulder dress by Ralph Lauren , Deepika Padukone attended the Golden Globes after party. Celebrity stylist Elizabeth Saltzman styled her for this event. With her hair styled side-ways with retro waves, she looked absolutely stunning donning this look. 
We think she looked great in this choice of colour! Share your views on the same by commenting below. 7 TAGS
